that Jehovah will soon bring about.

01:02:01.572 --> 01:02:04.908 line:90% position:50% align:center
Please join in singing
the original song

01:02:04.908 --> 01:02:07.035 line:90% position:50% align:center
“Peace at Last!”

01:02:07.035 --> 01:02:09.746 line:90% position:50% align:center
